description:
Danny recaps part 2 of The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion, which featured more Erika questions, a snoozy Dorit package, an emotional Kath and Kyle, and more! Then Danny dips into Winter House and has a brief chat with Ariana Madix from Vanderpump Rules about the new season. Unfortunately, some audio issues caused a shorter than expected chat, but she does touch on the Brock of it all, Lala, and more.
